{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/the-witchs-throne-mengalahkan-penyihir/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Witch’s Throne: Petualangan Mengalahkan Penyihir Dalam Ramalan","content":"<p>Setiap 10 tahun sekali, seorang gadis akan berubah menjadi penyihir jahat dan mencoba menghancurkan dunia. Seluruh makhluk terancam dengan kehgadiran sosok penyihir yang tengah mempersiapkan rencananya di sebuah takhta yang menjulang tinggi. Namun bagi setiap orang, perjalanan mengalahkan penyihir menjadi kesempatan untuk mencari petualangan yang mengasyikkan!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48231\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48231\" data-attachment-id=\"48231\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/the-witchs-throne-mengalahkan-penyihir/attachment/01-the-witchs-throne/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-the-witch&#8217;s-throne\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-48231 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" alt=\"The Witch’s Throne\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48231\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Hal ini pula yang dirasakan oleh Agni Arvelle, tokoh utama dari komik The Witch’s Throne.The Witch’s Throne karya komikus Cedric Caballes adalah satu dari sekian banyak komik baru di CIAYO Comics yang bekerja sama dengan kanal komik internasional Tapas. Di CIAYO Comics, kamu bisa membaca The Witch’s Throne dalam bahasa Indonesia secara cuma-cuma!</p>\n<p>Kembali ke cerita, sejak kecil Agni memiliki ambisi untuk mengalahkan sang penyihir yang tiba-tiba muncul. Di usia 9 tahun, Agni mulai belajar ilmu alkemi, bahkan sampai 10 tahun tidak keluar rumah. Kedua lengannya saja hanya tinggal tulang belulang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48232\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48232\" data-attachment-id=\"48232\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/the-witchs-throne-mengalahkan-penyihir/attachment/02-the-witchs-throne/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-the-witch&#8217;s-throne\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48232\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48232\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Tingkah kupernya tak menghalangi Agni untuk berkelana dan mengikuti sebuah kompetisi prestisius. Demi mengalahkan penyihir, Agni harus bisa membuktikan kemampuannya dalam kompetisi untuk mencari anggota tim pemburu penyihir.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48233\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48233\" data-attachment-id=\"48233\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/the-witchs-throne-mengalahkan-penyihir/attachment/03-the-witchs-throne/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-the-witch&#8217;s-throne\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48233\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48233\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun, sejak kemunculan penyihir, tatanan masyarakat telah berubah drastis. Semua orang diberikan pekerjaan dan level yang sudah ditentukan untuk mengukur kelayakan bertarung dengan pemnyihir. Agar bisa hidup makmur, mereka harus menjalani pekerjaan mereka dan menaikkan level. Mereka yang sudah mencapai level 99 dapat berpartisipasi dalam kompetisi perburuan penyihir.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48234\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48234\" data-attachment-id=\"48234\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/the-witchs-throne-mengalahkan-penyihir/attachment/04-the-witchs-throne/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-the-witch&#8217;s-throne\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48234\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-the-witchs-throne-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48234\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam perjalanannya, Agni bertemu dengan banyak orang menarik seperti bandit, pandai besi, serta orc bertubuh besar. Siapa yang akan jadi kawan dan jadi lawan Agni? Akankah Agni memenuhi mimpinya mengalahkan sang penyihir? Ikuti kisah The Witch’s Throne, setiap hari Jumat pukul 20:00 WIB <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-witchs-throne\">hanya di CIAYO Comics!</a> Jangan lupa juga untuk <em>subscribe</em> biar kamu nggak ketinggalan <em>update</em> episode terbarunya! Kamu punya komik petualangan atau komik fantasi sendiri dan ingin kamu terbitkan? Ikuti <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-comics-challenge-vol-3-total-hadiahnya-450-juta-rupiah/\">CIAYO Comics Challenge Vol. 3</a>dengan total hadiah 450 juta Rupiah!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"6ba0eebf-7e34-528d-93bd-f5415e6c8615"}}}